# 解答

```java
class Solution {
    public int maximumSwap(int num) {
        List<Integer>list=new ArrayList<>();
        String string=String.valueOf(num);
        int len=string.length();
        char[]chars=string.toCharArray();
        for (int i = 0; i < len; i++) {
            list.add(chars[i]-'0');
        }
        Collections.sort(list);
        Collections.reverse(list);
        int big;
        for (int i = 0; i < len; i++) {
            if(list.get(i)!=chars[i]-'0'){
                big=list.get(i);
                char ch= (char) ('0'+big);
                int index=0;
                for (int j = len-1; j >= i+1; j--) {
                    if(chars[j]==ch){
                        index=j;
                        break;
                    }
                }
                char temp=chars[index];
                chars[index]=chars[i];
                chars[i]=temp;
                return Integer.valueOf(String.copyValueOf(chars));
            }
        }
        return num;
    }
}
```

- time:*O(n^2^)*
- space:*O(n)*

