> - 链表中节点数目在范围 `[0, 300]` 内
> - `-100 <= Node.val <= 100`
> - 题目数据保证链表已经按升序 **排列**

# 代码

```java
class Solution {
    public ListNode deleteDuplicates(ListNode head) {
        if(head==null||head.next==null){
            return head;
        }
        ListNode last=head,p=last.next;
        while(p.next!=null) {//p不是最后一个
            if (p.val == last.val) {
                last.next = p.next;
            }else{
                last = p;
            }
            p = p.next;
        }
        if(p.val==last.val){
            last.next=null;
        }
        return head;
    }
}
```

- time:*O(n)*

- space:*O(1)*

